autorenew.description:
Subscribe to automatic renewal

It is important to understand the following points:

  1. When the plan expires, the feature will be renewed automatically.
  2. The amount deducted will continue according to the selected plan.
  3. Any transaction will automatically generate a new receipt, issued from your account.
  4. Cancellation of this service may be performed at any time using the subscription management interface.
  5. If rates change, you will receive an email escrowing the changes. You can decide at this time if you wish to continue the service.
